des:
Have you heard of magical creatures named weredogs, listen to this story in many episodes about a weredog named Vanilla as he ponders about his origins on Earth, his life at Star Fleet Academy and the menace of were mice. Stay tuned for new episodes.
You can say stop and help at any point.
